metadata.name: Mezzanine
metadata.description: Genesis by Lauren Michelle is a Musical NFT with rarity within the sound. The audio bites are pieces of her musical selections from her VR performance in 2022. This token is verifiable for admission to her VR performance in 2022. The orchestra tier has an unlockable of a VR headset and Red Carpet boarding to metaverse platforms. The minting of these NFTS do not give any holders or minters of the NFTS any IP rights.
